# Group Bills
Represents the bills introduced in the both the senate and house

---
**Bill attributes:**
- id `(String)` : Id of bill.
- title `(String)` : Name of bill.
- sponsor `(List)` : Main sponsor of the bill.
- date_introduced `(String)` : Date the bill was introduced.
- chamber `(String)` : Which chamber of congress member is part of.
- voted_house `(String)` : Was the bill voted on in the house.
- voted_senate `(String)` : Was the bill voted on in the senate.
- passed_house `(String)` : Did the bill pass in the house?
- passed_senate `(String)` : Did the bill pass in the senate?

---
## Bill Collection [bills]
### List all bills [GET]
Retrieve all bills introduced during the current congress.

